| Item | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| App title with keywords | ✅ | "Rozze" — consider adding subtitle keywords |
| Subtitle (don't leave empty) | ⚠️ Check | Make sure it's filled in App Store Connect |
| App description (hook in first 2 lines) | ⚠️ Check | Verify the first 2 lines hook readers |
| Keywords researched and added | ⚠️ Check | journal, mood, audio, diary, gratitude, mindfulness |
| Screenshots (show benefits, not features) | ✅ | Previously captured in conversation `48128f07` |
| App preview video (optional but helps) | ❌ Optional | Consider adding one for higher conversion |
| Privacy policy URL | ⚠️ Check | Must be set in App Store Connect |
| Support URL | ⚠️ Check | `https://rozze.vercel.app/` should work |
